  <h2>Overview</h2> 
  <p>A Rich Text Editor (RTE) provides the ability to enter text with markup. </p> 
  <p>For Communities components, while similar to the <a href="../../sites/authoring/using/rich-text-editor.md">rich text editor in the author environment</a>, it affects text entered in the publish environment.</p> 
  <img imageRotate="0" src="assets/chlimage_1-410.png" /> 
  <h2>Enabling Rich Text Editor</h2> 
  <p>Communities components that allow user generated content (UGC) can be enabled to allow RTE. Depending on whether the component was added to a page or included within a <a href="../../communities/using/functions.md">function</a>, RTE may or may not be enabled by default.</p> 
  <p>If not enabled, simply enter <a href="../../communities/using/sites-console.md#authoringsitecontent">author edit mode</a>, select the component for edit, and select the <span class="code">Rich Text Editor</span> checkbox.</p> 
  <p>RTE is available for the following Communities components:</p> 
  <ul> 
   <li><a href="../../communities/using/blog-feature.md">blog</a></li> 
   <li><a href="../../communities/using/calendar.md">calendar</a></li> 
   <li><a href="../../communities/using/comments.md">comments</a></li> 
   <li><a href="../../communities/using/file-library.md">filelibrary</a></li> 
   <li><a href="../../communities/using/forum.md">forum</a></li> 
   <li><a href="../../communities/using/configure-messaging.md">messaging</a></li> 
   <li><a href="../../communities/using/working-with-qna.md">QnA</a></li> 
   <li><a href="../../communities/using/reviews.md">reviews</a></li> 
  </ul> 
  <h2>Customization</h2> 
  <p>Customization of the rich text editor is possible as the implementation is based on <a href="http://www.ckeditor.com/">CKEditor</a>.</p> 
  <p>The current configuration for Communities components is in the <span class="code">cq.social. 
    <g class="gr_ gr_13 gr-alert gr_spell gr_inline_cards gr_disable_anim_appear ContextualSpelling ins-del multiReplace" data-gr-id="13" id="13">
      scf 
    </g> 
    <g class="gr_ gr_14 gr-alert gr_spell gr_inline_cards gr_disable_anim_appear ContextualSpelling ins-del multiReplace" data-gr-id="14" id="14">
      clientlib 
    </g></span>, located in the repository at</p> 
  <p style="margin-left: 40px;"><span class="code">/libs/clientlibs/social/commons/scf/ckrte.js</span></p> 
  <p>Modifying the cq.social.scf clientlib is not recommended as future upgrades may override any edits.</p> 
  <h3>Example Customization : Inline Links</h3> 
  <p>Due to security concerns, the hyperlink options are not included in the set of rich text icons presented to members by default. The ability for mischief is extensive when hrefs are allowed in UGC.</p> 
  <p>To add the hyperlink options to the toolbar :</p> 
  <ul> 
   <li>add a toolbar named "<span class="code">links</span>" 
    <ul> 
     <li><span class="code">{ name: 'links', items : [ 'Link','Unlink','Anchor' ] }</span></li> 
    </ul> </li> 
   <li>select <strong>Save All</strong></li> 
  </ul> 
  <h4>/libs/clientlibs/social/commons/scf/ckrte.js</h4> 
  <codeblock gutter="true" class="syntax js">
    CKRte.prototype.config&amp;nbsp;=&amp;nbsp;{!!discoiqbr!!&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;toolbar:&amp;nbsp;[!!discoiqbr!!&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;{&amp;nbsp;name:&amp;nbsp;"basicstyles",!!discoiqbr!!&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;items:&amp;nbsp;["Bold",&amp;nbsp;"Italic",&amp;nbsp;"Underline",&amp;nbsp;"NumberedList",&amp;nbsp;"BulletedList",&amp;nbsp;"Outdent",&amp;nbsp;"Indent",&amp;nbsp;"JustifyLeft",&amp;nbsp;"JustifyCenter",&amp;nbsp;"JustifyRight",&amp;nbsp;"JustifyBlock",&amp;nbsp;"TextColor"]!!discoiqbr!!&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;},!!discoiqbr!!&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;{&amp;nbsp;name:&amp;nbsp;'links',&amp;nbsp;!!discoiqbr!!&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;items&amp;nbsp;:&amp;nbsp;[&amp;nbsp;'Link','Unlink','Anchor'&amp;nbsp;]&amp;nbsp;!!discoiqbr!!&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;}!!discoiqbr!!&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;],!!discoiqbr!!&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;autoParagraph:&amp;nbsp;false,!!discoiqbr!!&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;autoUpdateElement:&amp;nbsp;false,!!discoiqbr!!&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;removePlugins:&amp;nbsp;"elementspath",!!discoiqbr!!&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;resize_enabled:&amp;nbsp;false!!discoiqbr!!}; 
  </codeblock> 
